				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11179317#post-4681712</guid>
				<title>nice hook</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11179317/a-non-prophet-organization-hub#post-4681712</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2020 22:48:45 +0000</pubDate>
								<wikidot:authorUserId>6259651</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I haven't heard of SAPPHIRE before now, but damn this is a beautifully powerful hook. The hub page gave me goosebumps at how intriguing it is. Religion is touchy AF, but this take on militant atheism applied to the SCP universe sounds oh-so fascinating, having the toxic bickering and violence of IRL religious conflict and seeing how to plays out in the anomalous world. Upvote for sure.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
